2017;;Breath;;Australian;;Simon Baker;;Elizabeth Debicki, Simon Baker, Richard Roxburgh;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Breath_(2017_film);;The film is set in the 1970s and two teenage boys form a connection with an older surfer.[1] The boys Pikelet and Loonie have grown up in a small town and through surfing met up with Sando, who challenges them to take greater and more dangerous risks.[2]